{"tid":949342,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"棋靈王=鮑姐","createTime":"2018-12-20T17:25:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:29:05.000Z","uid":88374,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbb44a7f3fe44f76f9e20ec3eb94eba7c080d8c","tid":949342,"uid":88374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"首先開個po<br />\n拎自己同ali比較<br />\n突顯自己仍有市場<br />\n<br />\n然後再開個ac提出更好既選擇（周慧敏 溫碧霞）<br />\n於是乎引來更多人恥笑自己<br />\n但同時又再買多3個ac<br />\n之後自己就開新po<br />\n用呢三個ac回覆「鮑姐」<br />\n達到bin屍效果<br />\n<br />\n重複以上動作超過十次<br />\n當其他連登仔見到頭三個回覆都係鮑姐時<br />\n就覺得好搞鬼<br />\n於是乎有樣學樣<br />\n<br />\n但如果頭三個回覆長期都係一樣<br />\n俾人質疑係開分身<br />\n啲分身就可以話：鬥快binc唔得？黎避免懷疑<br />\n又可以帶起鬥快覆鮑姐呢個潮流<br />\n<br />\n於是乎鮑姐每開一個po<br />\n下面就會鬥快覆鮑姐<br />\n咁成個po就會極速被推至熱門<br />\n亦由於夠搞鬼而引來更多人認識/google鮑姐<br />\n最後成功爭取人氣<br />\n<br />\n所以話成班child登仔俾鮑姐利用左都唔知...<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LXKW0X7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLXKW0X7.jpg&h=537ed673&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a110e35fc4efc0d626833fde1d8ebba9b5ae548d","tid":949342,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"tldr"},{"pid":"7fc98bca281993cfb3dd3f24156a6c079b25760d","tid":949342,"uid":101591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5edee096a47dab288686f66c4b23871cd00bf8ae","tid":949342,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:29:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9be0a5e73830e83095acaa27a605c0e1273aac9","tid":949342,"uid":56610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T17:30:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mgMVw6p.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmgMVw6p.gif&h=afe201b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a540b9befd965db4fe9bc842d96ed24730599216","tid":949342,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"genius<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d3fa8987dca0957e77f035f221db25f4ceed28","tid":949342,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:12:42.000Z","msg":"樓主會唔會又係鮑姐分身，反宣傳自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d383e4e4898c30ef553ff48c6e9591bd61eba82f","tid":949342,"uid":18020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:03:37.000Z","msg":"條撚屌借鮑姐上位<br />\n家下想畫清界線"},{"pid":"7f385f6d34e66002147d587197b98244ebc27c1e","tid":949342,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:21:03.000Z","msg":"樓主=鮑姐<br />\n開個ac懶係揭露鮑姐陰謀<br />\n吸引更多人討論聲討鮑姐<br />\n鮑姐知名度又高左<br />\n臭閪樓主"},{"pid":"7db4f0c6acf5804a1ddb0d1b9b9812efaf3ea112","tid":949342,"uid":88374,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a540b9befd965db4fe9bc842d96ed24730599216","tid":949342,"uid":214784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:03:51.000Z","msg":"genius<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea6469f55be61e1583f92c557b218d3c1a1ad8c","tid":949342,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T02:29:05.000Z","msg":"結論 樓主=鮑姐"}]}